Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(800,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.23,0:00:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.35,0:00:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.08,0:00:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.43,0:01:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Battle Ship Takes Off!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.44,0:01:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Domino Stadium...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.40,0:01:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The stage only the chosen tournament finalists will know the location of.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, several have gathered to fight for the title of Duel King.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just seven more to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other man who holds a God Card, Seto Kaiba, was the first to arrive, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Rishid...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't forgotten the agreement you made with my father, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to put an end to the cursed inheritance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that my family has suffered for the past 3,000 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By taking Yugi's {\i1}life{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Ancient Egypt, the Pharaohs forced their subjects to build pyramids...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These pyramids were shaped like solidified beams of light pointed towards the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The were a monument to the Pharaoh's absolute power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But one day, a man who worshiped {\i1}darkness{\i0} came forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a war...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Court Magicians created seven items to seal the darkness away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them, the Millennium Puzzle, is in the shape of a reverse pyramid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the symbol of darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to protect the seal on that darkness, my family suffered massive losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is written in the prophecy handed down in my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"An evil power was sealed in darkness along with the spirit of a young Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But after thousands of years of slumber,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the evil power will rise once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when that happens, the Pharaoh's soul will awaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will wander this world seeking the memories he has lost."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And only I know how to find these memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never give him his memories back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the power of the Sun God Ra to bury Yugi back in the world of darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only way I'll ever be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isono, turn on the stadium lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim the lights at the stands!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn the lights above the stands on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, Yugi and the others are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the location of the finals?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it still under construction?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we really gonna do it {\i1}here{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have discovered the location of the tournament finals...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We recognize you three as participants in the final tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of {\i1}course{\i0} you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We congratulate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept these I.D. cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where are the other finalists?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, only Seto-{\i1}sama{\i0} and the three of you have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only four remain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Malik is among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:05:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So a new Duelist has shown himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he Malik?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it isn't Namu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you two as well! I'm so glad you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright after what happened before...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right when this guy asked me tips on Dueling, the Ghouls attacked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And how come this guy's all safe and sound when we got captured?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they didn't bother with {\i1}me{\i0} since I don't have any rare cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And all those crazy incidents happened after we met this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could he be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Namu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He tried to save us when we were being attacked by the Ghouls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Jounouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honor to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Namu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It takes more than luck to win and get {\i1}this{\i0} far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well with so many tough looking people here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I just lost my self-esteem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I thinking too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's {\i1}he{\i0} here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}, is your wound alright now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa told me on the phone that you were in critical condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should take him back to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd he even get here with his body in the shape it's in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}! That Duel Disk...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it's so I can participate in the tournament finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-What?!\N -What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:07:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, I see you managed to gather enough Puzzle Cards in such a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe Bakura-{\i0}kun'{\i1}s actually participating in the final tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the heck did you even {\i1}enter{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than that, you even won six Puzzle Cards to qualify?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It {\b0}can't{\b1} be...! Again...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's the seventh Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's... Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's the owner of Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are {\i1}you{\i0} Malik?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}bastard{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way in {\i1}hell{\i0} I'll let you off the hook!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we meet once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna beat the hell outta you right here and now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd rather settle this fair and square in a Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik of the tournament's evil organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm free to disqualify you from this tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But rather than do that now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat you to a bloody pulp and take your God Card away from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My big brother's gonna take revenge for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even I could feel his tremendous fighting spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the seven Duelists please give me your attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an announcement to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you have won in the prelims and assembled here at the final location, Domino Stadium.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this will {\i1}not{\i0} be the location of the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real stage should appear before us momentarily...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's {\i1}that{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A blimp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the place of the finals?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's called... the Battle Ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle Ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tournament finals will take place 1,000 meters in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now please board.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will take off once the eight Duelist arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At 7 sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dueling in the sky sounds pretty fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mhm-hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the Ghouls can't touch us 1,000 meters in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm pumped now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go in, Shizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! You can't board without an I.D. card!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-No way!\N -You're {\i1}kidding{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was looking forward to watching my brother Duel in the final tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you let it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, {\i1}c'mon{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"No" means no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! {\i1}I{\i0} don't have an I.D. card either!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let them ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Mokuba-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll accept your kind words!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just pretend you didn't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set the blimp off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still don't have eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't depart without-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ones holding the God Cards have already gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need eight for the tournament to run smoothly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle Ship, take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You can see all of Domino City from up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing to be able to Duel all the way up in the sky, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess strong Duelists can even fly through the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't take much to excite {\i1}some{\i0} people, Deadbeat Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Deadbeat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deadbeat, meaning {\i1}average{\i0} at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll {\i1}freeze up{\i0} when you face the more challenging Duels that lie ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better enjoy the feeling of being a tourist while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That {\b0}bastard{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I swear to God I'm gonna kick his {\b0}ass{\b1} in this tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, let me give you one piece of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In one of the Battle City Preliminary matches, 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you left your God Card out of your deck, for whatever foolish reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed this while working with you in that Tag Duel against the Ghouls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! I will {\i1}not{\i0} accept that during our fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this final tournament, we are about to step foot into the domain of the gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner will be {\i1}determined{\i0} by the three God Cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fight that will go down in legend is about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}will{\i0} beat you and Malik, obtain the three God Cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and become the world's strongest Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have arranged rooms for all eight Duelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may access them with your Identification Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tournament will begin in one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The match-ups will be announced at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This room is really pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see the night view really well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... It's the street lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, do you remember your promise to take me to the ocean again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun shining on the ocean water is beautiful too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I started to think I'd never get to see such a beautiful view with my big brother ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:14:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I got to finally see such a lovely view again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, you'll get to see tons of beautiful scenes like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just you watch, Shizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll win straight through the tournament with the courage you gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time I'll fight Yugi in a fair match and become a True Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! This is a nice room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gah! Why the hell did you guys just prance on in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cheering section wasn't given rooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! The fridge is packed with food and drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starved!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's even room service!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone but Shizuka GET OUT!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh c'mon, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more fun with everyone here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"F-Fun"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka, Duelists {\i1}need{\i0} a little nervousness before a Duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll ask Shizuka-{\i0}chan{\i1} if she wants to look at the beautiful view with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}, the view sure is pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn you{\i0}, Otogi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey look! You can see Domino Pier from up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this coulda been time for you to spend with Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo Honda, if you know that why don't you to to a {\i1}different{\i0} room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like {\i1}Yugi's{\i0} room, for example...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, Yugi's busy preparing for his Duels, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bother him right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Duelist {\i1}too{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh {\i1}yeah{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My {\i1}god{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Honda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For bringing Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Don't worry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just {\i1}win{\i0}, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing outside my brother's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The eight Duelist just arrived moments ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wanted to inform him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know how important the time before a Duel is to a Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I humbly beg your forgiveness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The tournament is finally starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will beat both Yugi and Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then I'll be sure to add the three God Cards to my personal collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The members of this group should prove to be fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I failed to achieve what I wanted back in Duelist Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this time around I'll win the tournament and fame!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot afford to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For our family, and for Lord Malik as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, I'm {\b0}happy{\b1} to have become one of your {\b0}friends{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a good thing I made arrangements prior to our meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Due to the fragment of myself still within that girl, I can control her whenever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And as for the other one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't get rid of the evil mind inside him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I brainwashed his outer persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything is in place!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The glyphs carved onto my back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Written in my flesh is the location of your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I won't let you have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll condemn you to eternal darkness with a Dark Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And when {\b0}I{\b1} obtain the three God Cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll become the {\b0}new{\b1} Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's my ultimate goal in this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now the battle of 1,000 years has begun, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My other self is searching for the pieces of his memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we must win in order to accomplish that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Osiris the Heaven Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A God Card...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I better put the God Card in my deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally starting... a fateful battle for the other me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When this battle is won... will I really regain my memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have to fight the possessor of a Millennium Item, the owner of Ra card...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the owner of Obelisk, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:19:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A battle of three gods clashing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I {\b0}will{\b1} win it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's two things bothering me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them is Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0} enter the tournament finals?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did he obtain a Duel Disk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not enough {\b0}blood{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a brief moment before, Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0} seemed like 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was being controlled by his dark personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are a duelist of the Dark Games, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bakura? I'm not Bakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is your objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi... you should know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever gets all the Millennium Items will have everything he wants from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forgive me, Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it can't be the evil being of the Millennium Ring,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0} said he threw it away at the Duelist Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't underestimate the dark powers of the Millennium Items.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bakura may once again be under the control of that being.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So what else is bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the eight Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody knows who it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was just thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder who exactly this person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first round of the tournament will now begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All participating Duelists and everyone else, please assemble in the central assembly hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Yup!\N -Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:20:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\i1}beating{\i0} that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Namu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we end up fighting in the first round,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,take it easy on me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the kind of Duelist who'd ease up because I'm fighting a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then when the time comes, let's give it our all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter {\b0}who{\b1} I fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if it's Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I {\b0}will{\b1} win!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's go, Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(137,137)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi and Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0} are chosen to fight in the first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do feel bad for Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}, but this Duel will be a {\i1}breeze{\i0} for Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They fight one another in the Duel Ring aligned with harsh wind from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s acting a bit strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:21:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah?! That's the Millennium Ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's being controlled by the Millennium Ring again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The First Sky Duel: Yugi VS Dark Bakura"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.14,0:22:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
